Class GraphicCell

  • java.lang.Object
    • bfsztg_gui.GraphicCell

  • public class GraphicCell
extends java.lang.Object
    A class with enums for the terrain, unit and marker types. It is used during the drawing of the hexagonal map.
    Author:
    fhenrir
